   Li, Xintian, Hong Kong Baptist Univ, Fac Sci, Hong Kong, Peoples R China.
   Chen, Xiaodie, East China Univ Sci \& Technol, Engn Res Ctr Pharmaceut Proc Chem, Sch Pharm, Minist Educ, Shang Hai 200237, Peoples R China.
   Huang, Rong, Wenzhou Acad Agr Sci, Zhejiang Key Lab Agrifood Resources \& High value U, Wenzhou 325006, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.bios.2026.118595},
